The paper deals with enhancing mobile data offloading, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses caching and prefetching, which are topics related to data management and storage, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.DC (Databases) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions delay-sensitive traffic, which is a topic related to multimedia and real-time systems, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category. Finally, the paper discusses the robustness of the procedures, which is a topic related to control and optimization, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category.
